Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:35.94,ED Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,The Claws of a Crab Can Snip Through a Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:39.57,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Isn't this a crab, Gin-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:41.67,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:42.61,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}One of Gran's old friends
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:45.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}gave her so many that she's sick of eating them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:47.45,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}so she's sharing the wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.66,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:50.92,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's been forever since I've had crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:52.77,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.33,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She only gave us one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:57.94,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she asked me how many I wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:00.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I told her I wanted a boxful...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.09,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Damn hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:05.03,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she giving us riddles like the Sphinx?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:06.58,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't Ikkyu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:09.85,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna "riddle me that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.65,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:12.83,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:15.11,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why a crab has so many legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:17.99,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So we can share them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:21.20,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Since the beginning of time, humans have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,fought many foolish wars over crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:24.89,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Such as the Battle of Sekigahara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:26.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Battle of Okehazama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.25,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's news to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:31.55,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the Holy Crab in Heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:32.81,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's a Holy Crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.50,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How did God turn into a crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.65,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Gave crabs more legs to end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:39.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the tragic conflicts and allow us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:41.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to eat crab together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.15,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,However, crabs could no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,move forwards or backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:49.90,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is it right to force the Holy Crab to live a sideways life?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.20,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is it right to force him to purely go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:53.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,scissors without any missionary or doggy style?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.77,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This conversation has gotten very weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.31,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:02:59.68,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of all the fighting over food,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:00.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,like whenever we have a hot pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:02.71,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.91,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's share this crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.85,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If we include the claws, this thing has ten legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.33,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty for everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.88,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But how do we split ten legs between three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.09,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,One will be left over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.67,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.04,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:57.42,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)\pos(732,75)}Power outage at Yorozuya
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:19.04,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(433,453)}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We were getting to the good part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:22.39,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check the circuit breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:24.99,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.21,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.42,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're already out of steam after the Four Devas arc?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:31.96,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop slackin' off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.60,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this was in the manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.98,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The author was overwhelmed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,with that one-shot collection business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.10,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:39.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't be doing one-shots
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,if he kept slackin' on his main series, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.22,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.78,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Super Legend, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.99,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of one-shots from big shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.02,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,One of those guys clearly doesn't fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.60,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There's a gorilla in the mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.40,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,And he was unabashed about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:53.46,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too cocky, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.64,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.63,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I just checked the circuit breaker and it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.82,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Power's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.05,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get started then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.42,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:08.30,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The Holy Crab was injured during the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.73,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he bumped into the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.60,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a leg is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.72,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:18.66,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not evil enough to steal food while the power's out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:19.72,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It obviously wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:20.92,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So it was one of you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.32,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.88,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You probably swiped the leg
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.14,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,when you were pretending to go check the circuit breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.31,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You said ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.89,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You probably cut yourself on the crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.77,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I hit my head on the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:30.87,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.95,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible to eat one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,of those shelled monsters in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:40.03,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we have a number that divides perfectly into three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:45.87,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The Holy Crab must have been trying to stop us from fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.89,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, enough bickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.14,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Each of us gets three legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.32,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You only get two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:54.51,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Your mouth is bleeding because you didn't remove the shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.61,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How desperate were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.44,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.46,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,When we were trashing that Legends mess during the blackout,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,a gorilla appeared and punched me hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.70,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Who would believe that story?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.53,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The missing crab leg was also him, I'm guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.43,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.95,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He must be completely stressed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:12.46,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.34,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, another blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:28.09,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(729,75)}Power outage at Yorozuya
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.85,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, don't move an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.24,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,One more time and you're gonna get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.77,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, it wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:19.91,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Cross my heart and hope to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:20.92,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.40,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know when the gorilla will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:24.85,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:25.94,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.09,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's wrong, Kagura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.73,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-Kagura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.97,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,My eye... My eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.21,Main-Alt,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,42)}Hold on, Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:36.71,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.85,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You just have a cut on your eyelid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.16,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,A gorilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:43.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A weird gorilla showed up and took a crab leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.94,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to stop it... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:47.61,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Shinpachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:50.10,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It took another crab leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.99,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is all Legend Gorilla's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.42,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:54.75,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:57.92,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,There's blood on the claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.55,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just cut your eye
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,on the claw when you tried
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to eat a crab leg in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:03.92,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.26,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,The gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:09.05,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,The gorilla grabbed the crab and stabbed me with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.68,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you're talking with your mouth full.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:12.79,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:16.60,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I fought back and bit off the gorilla's crotch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:17.84,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn gorilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That should teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.43,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:23.55,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop blaming the gorilla for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:26.07,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's so obvious that you ate those crab legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.61,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No, we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.20,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,It was the gorilla. The gorilla ate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:33.26,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You refuse to own up, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.29,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:40.40,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use a candle to prevent any further cheating
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,if the power goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.68,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:45.00,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Should have done this earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.01,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I ever cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.58,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't cheat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:50.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but this should keep that gorilla away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:52.86,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Since gorillas are afraid of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.40,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll divide up the legs so we can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:57.27,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.85,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.35,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I like the tougher meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:04.15,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that should put an end to their thievery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.59,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,If the power goes out, we'll still have light from the candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:09.72,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Most importantly, the crab is in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:12.68,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the power went out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.30,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.24,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.82,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check the circuit breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.08,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.07,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna borrow a candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.30,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.76,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They're leaving me alone with the crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.51,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The crab is undefended!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:33.90,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.42,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Or are they letting me have my way with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:37.52,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is the perfect chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.56,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I should go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:41.46,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They already swiped two legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.74,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.03,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.98,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any legs left...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.24,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This candle won't light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:51.99,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This one won't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:52.81,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nor this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:53.93,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.99,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,These aren't candles...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.37,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,They're crab legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.37,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.70,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.88,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I realized how foolish I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:08.23,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,When I chose to focus on how to divide the legs among three people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:11.35,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How to squirrel the extra leg away from them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.03,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:16.39,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I lost before I even sat down at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:21.39,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They never had any intention of sharing a single crab leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:24.65,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,My tiny claw could never pierce
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,through their shamelessly thick shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.22,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I will never stand a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:33.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,until I bring out my own giant claws
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.79,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,for plundering the entire world of every last crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:41.10,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with all the outages?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:44.56,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to get this crab party started again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:45.25,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.59,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Only the body and claws are left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.09,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's done is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.59,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to mistake crab legs for candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.25,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,In what world would you find people who
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:56.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,mistake crab legs for candles?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:09:00.18,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shinpachi's fault for leaving the crab legs next to the candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.73,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And you're trying to shift the blame to me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:02.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of apologizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:05.43,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was an honest mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:06.62,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.75,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mature, Gin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:09.86,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shinpachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.22,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Divide the crab into three equal portions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:17.49,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How can you people have the gall to talk about equal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.06,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hit them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.44,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Punch them in the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:23.62,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But if I lose my cool now, they'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:26.93,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They've been trying to goad me into snapping
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:28.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,with their heavy-handed behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:31.15,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.76,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You guys already ate eight crab legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.23,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Three equal portions, my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.84,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:37.78,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they want me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.78,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll have a response prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.35,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:45.30,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Two of the legs were eaten by that gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.92,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We each ate three of the remaining six.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.10,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,By mistake, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.98,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to someone else's mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:54.29,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can have the two claws with the tougher meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.76,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But we're sharing the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.37,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They'll use some kind of absurd logic to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,declare that two claws are equal to four legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:06.25,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he said that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:08.36,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.54,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I like the tougher meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.21,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He was trying to inflate the value of the claws
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.21,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,as part of his strategy to fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.55,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:21.21,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The claw may look like it has more than a leg,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:23.69,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,but in reality, it's the same amount of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.76,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That guy was feigning interest in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the claws so he could be rid of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.03,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He'll use the claws to distract
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,me while he aims straight for the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:42.69,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.33,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.03,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:49.95,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you guys have the claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.58,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I'm stuck with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:55.32,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.76,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He's using my statement about the claws
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,against me, to lock me down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.96,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Despite all my taunting,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:05.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,he's stayed calm and seen right through my plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.53,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,completely ignoring the claws
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:09.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and going straight for the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.98,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And he's pretending that he's doing us a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.19,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,by taking the body so he can win over the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:18.90,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,A technique practiced by dads around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:22.75,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the body cause it's all squishy and gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:23.95,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:26.80,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But if you like crab legs so much, I'll take the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:29.32,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the body of a crab is disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.50,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Women and children tend to avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:33.38,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But the dad knows
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:39.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,that the body contains Princess Crab-Paste!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:41.13,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shi-Shinpachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:43.25,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You already know the secret of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Crab-Paste at such a young age?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.52,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Princess Crab-Paste is the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,ugliest woman of the Sengoku period.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.60,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you know that her repulsive face hides...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:57.82,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,...the finest lay of the Sengoku period!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:02.11,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, you may have won some small skirmishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:04.62,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,but you haven't won the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.57,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You must take the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:08.42,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Take Princess Crab-Paste...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.99,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,if you wish to become a Crabqueror!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:15.38,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the one who conquers the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:19.25,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Crab-Paste!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.22,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:24.09,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Everything will be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:27.01,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The Shimura army will keep you safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.47,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The Sakata army approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.55,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It is too dangerous here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:32.23,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We must escape at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.36,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:37.98,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:40.57,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Pr-Princess Crab-Paste...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.19,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Crab-Paste?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:46.57,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.89,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.47,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't just Princess Crab-Paste!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:53.41,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The body is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.42,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,...completely empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.38,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry, Shinpachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:00.64,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I took the meat from the body and cooked it with rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.76,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I saved the crab paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:09.39,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cooked it with rice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:14.54,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate, General Shimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:17.80,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This castle belongs to the Sakata army now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:20.11,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And Princess Crab-Paste has fallen into our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:23.69,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This castle no longer holds any strategic value!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:24.92,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.11,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,General Sakata...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:31.08,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You anticipated that I would anticipate your plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:32.87,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.62,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But in war,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:39.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the key is to become a coward with multiple back-up plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.31,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.01,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He knew all along...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:46.47,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,...that my focus was on the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:51.30,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And to fool me, he restored the body after taking its contents,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.06,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and pretended to be Princess Crab-Paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:56.66,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, while I was falling into his trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:14:00.69,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,he was taking possession of the ultimate sword, Crabclaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:03.57,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry, Pachi-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.30,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We even took the claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.03,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You ended up without a single bite of crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.53,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I misjudged him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.66,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.93,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who let us have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:16.72,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You have sunk your fangs into the crab shell,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gintoki the Viper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:21.97,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll help myself then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:26.73,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.09,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The meat of the Crabclaw is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.85,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,The meat is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.35,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.77,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Da-Daigoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.73,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You're so weird, Gin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.65,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you like the claws so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:46.01,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,There's more meat in the leg below the claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:46.86,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Silly Gin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.66,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I spent too much time talking about claws!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:52.26,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Technically, the term claw only
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:54.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,refers to the pincer at the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:58.66,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I never expected her to divide up the claws like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:02.89,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I ignored you since I assumed you were just a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:05.21,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but you took advantage of my battle with General Shimura
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.42,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,to use my own words against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:11.21,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Daigoro, you are no ordinary Daigoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.72,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You were sent by Iga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.73,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.89,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,who intends to take advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,of the chaos and conquer this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.44,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,A true tactician would lay low until
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:29.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,he's already conquered the world in secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:30.82,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Viper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:34.11,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I grant you an eternal slumber inside that empty shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:39.64,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:43.87,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I can still conquer the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:47.17,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I may have lost the claws,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:50.88,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but I used the treasures of the castle to create a new paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.81,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Castle Crab-on-Rice belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.56,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And Princess Crab-Paste is in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:02.56,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I hold these, my ambition will never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:05.11,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Viper! Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.14,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,A castle is being constructed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:10.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,next to ours at an alarming pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.36,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.66,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Castle Crab-Juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:17.98,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:20.27,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This man has gathered his surviving forces
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and begun to build a castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:23.87,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.94,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,There's more to a crab than its meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.55,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Even the shell has its flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:29.89,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:32.78,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to pit leftover juices against my crab-on-rice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and reverse the situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.42,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This is your last chance to seek a peaceful resolution, Viper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:42.35,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Grant me the right to access Castle Crab-on-Rice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.56,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and meet with Princess Crab-Paste!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:45.66,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.92,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you seek to bargain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,on equal footing with me, the Crabqueror?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.56,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Who said anything about equal footing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.85,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I, Shimura Shinpachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:57.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,demand seventy percent of Castle Crab-on-Rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.93,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seventy percent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:01.70,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You overestimate what you hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.71,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You have dug your own grave, Viper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:08.18,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Crab on rice may sound delicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:12.72,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,but in reality, it barely tastes any different from plain rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:16.22,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, alone, crab on rice holds no power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:18.97,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Your castle serves as little more than decoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.08,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Crab on rice requires flavorful vegetables
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:23.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,which have been cooked in crab juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.61,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You can no longer survive
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Sengoku period without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.08,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:32.72,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You have underestimated the potency of my hand-salted rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.19,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.21,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Lord Viper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.83,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't enough flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:44.58,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.98,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Such firepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.54,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The crab juice is strong in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.40,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:54.30,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is like Gian vs. Nobita!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.62,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're a perfect match!\NThe ultimate combination!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.30,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Best friends forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.97,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, Viper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.22,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Time to let me take over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:05.65,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:09.02,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I have my own Doraemon in Princess Crab-Paste!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:12.86,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.19,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This shaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.45,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,It'll taste better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.79,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Tha-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:26.62,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.62,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.19,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,The castle in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:34.51,Main-Alt,Both,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,75)}Note: Referring to Laputa: Castle in the Sky the film written and directed by Hayao Miyazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.51,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Crab-Congee-Laputa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.41,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.51,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Castle Crab-on-Rice and Castle Crab-Juice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:42.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,were taken over and combined into one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:45.89,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She's stolen our cooking to create the ultimate recipe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:48.14,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and lay claim to the mantle of conqueror!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:50.19,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:53.02,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're no ordinary assassin of Iga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.03,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:58.28,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm neither Daigoro nor an assassin of Iga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:03.68,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,My true name is Kagura Crab Congee Laputa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.29,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,A descendant of the royal family
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:08.04,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,which ruled over the ancient city of Crab-Congee-Laputa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.67,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I have been waiting for this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:14.46,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,when you would unlock the path to Crab-Congee-Laputa,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.06,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,for I never could have
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:19.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,cooked crab on rice or vegetables in crab juice on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:21.70,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.76,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.55,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,In return, I shall give you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:27.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,a demonstration of the true power of crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:44.24,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,O-One egg can cause this much damage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:47.33,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,A little stirring and the smell has me drooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:51.33,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is the true power of crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.72,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.34,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Pr-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.12,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Crab-Paste!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:59.84,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting over crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.40,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,Crabs were never meant to create conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.13,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,Crabs are meant to bring everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,together around the table for a pleasant meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:12.06,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that your original intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.15,Main-Alt,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.86,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.86,Main-Alt,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The finest show on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:18.36,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,The three of you can share this meal together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.09,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:24.18,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Our souls are enraged by the long battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.87,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We can never bury this hatchet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:27.86,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,It will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:29.70,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,I will help to mend fences.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:34.56,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,The savory flavor of crab paste is gentle as the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.96,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that it will soothe your souls
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and restore your kind nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:46.19,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,Now, speak the words of unity and add me to the pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.52,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Balse appetit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.32,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:06.36,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You can have the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.89,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this crab party restarted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:18.41,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No, let's get this crab party started.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:20.50,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you have forty seconds to get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.90,Main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes too fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.69,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Imitation crab is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:45.32,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.99,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Crab-Flavored Sausage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:51.26,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,Band together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:56.52,Main,Paste,0000,0000,0000,,to eat cheap food!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:34.89,ED Title,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,People Forget to Return Stuff All the Time Without Even Realizing It
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:31.40,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:34.89,Main,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,People forget to return stuff all the time without even realizing it!